1
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,959
I definitely cured you last time.

2
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:56,840
You again?

3
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,879
What are you doing here?

4
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:02,640
Didn't you bring me here?

5
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,319
Can we agree on something?

6
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:07,040
Let's not start with a fight next time.

7
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:10,840
I'm warning you.

8
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:12,479
You have Deficiency of Qi and Blood.

9
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:14,000
If you force your Internal energy,

10
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,520
it'll only cause further damage to your body.

11
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,560
Last time was an Injury Penetrating the Meridians.

12
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:31,360
If I hadn't intervened in time,

13
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,800
you'd have turned into a mummy on a tree, unnoticed.

14
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:37,759
This time it's the Six Realms Ghost Poison.

15
00:02:39,639 --> 00:02:42,479
It clouds the mind and erodes bones without shedding blood.

16
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,080
Plus the Yin-Yang Mother-Child Gu.

17
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:47,479
Seriously, miss, what kind of high-risk job do you do?

18
00:02:47,479 --> 00:02:48,240
How much do you make a month?

19
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:52,120
Knowing too much won't do you any good.

20
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:08,759
I've suppressed the Gu worm for you again.

21
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,639
This Six Realms Ghost Poison isn't easy to cure.

22
00:03:12,479 --> 00:03:13,639
I managed to reduce its toxicity.

23
00:03:16,319 --> 00:03:17,360
Since you owe me such a huge favor,

24
00:03:18,479 --> 00:03:19,159
how about telling me

25
00:03:19,159 --> 00:03:20,039
the origins of that jade pendant?

26
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:28,199
Number 0, your consultation time is up. Return at once.

27
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:32,120
Or what my connection to the Xuanyi Society is?

28
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:34,840
Number 0, your consultation time is up. Return at once.

29
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,879
I'll waive the consultation fee.

30
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:42,719
Just keep my secret.

31
00:03:42,719 --> 00:03:44,080
And we'll call it even.

32
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:52,080
The consultation is over.

33
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:55,039
Contestants 0 and 1, please present your prescriptions.

34
00:03:56,560 --> 00:03:58,960
This is the Wo Kingdom's Six Realms Ghost Poison.

35
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:01,919
My prescription guarantees a flawless cure.

36
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,800
What about the Ancient Methods Faction?

37
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:14,479
Your prescription seems fine on the surface,

38
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,319
but unfortunately,

39
00:04:16,319 --> 00:04:17,439
it treats the symptoms, not the root cause.

40
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,120
And it leaves the patient with lifelong weakness.

41
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,639
You sure talk a big game.

42
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:25,439
Show us your prescription, then.

43
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:27,240
What's your trick this time?

44
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,839
My prescription

45
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:31,279
uses Ten Thousand Poison Gall,

46
00:04:31,279 --> 00:04:32,639
fighting poison with poison.

47
00:04:32,639 --> 00:04:34,199
Not only does it cure the poison,

48
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:36,560
it ensures the patient's long-term health.

49
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:49,879
Master Apothecary Ye,

50
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:50,839
your Ancient Methods Faction

51
00:04:50,839 --> 00:04:53,079
probably couldn't even identify the poison, could you?

52
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,240
Everyone,

53
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:58,079
Contestant 1's judgment is absolutely correct.

54
00:04:58,839 --> 00:05:01,439
This person is indeed poisoned by the Six Realms Ghost Poison.

55
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:04,480
This poison is composed of six different toxins.

56
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:06,279
Its toxicity is extremely complex.

57
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,360
Number 0,

58
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:10,160
you dare to fight poison with poison?

59
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,480
If the toxins clash,

60
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,800
that won't be saving her,

61
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,680
it will be killing her!

62
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,040
Whether it can cure the poison,

63
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,040
we'll know once we try.

64
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:16,720
Yes.

65
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:19,800
I don't think we need to waste any more time.

66
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,959
Contestant 1's prescription

67
00:05:20,959 --> 00:05:22,959
is exactly the antidote for the Six Realms Ghost Poison.

68
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,040
Please.

69
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,800
Master Apothecary Ye,

70
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:36,040
looks like your Ancient Methods Faction is losing again.

71
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:40,079
Don't celebrate too soon, Tech Faction.

72
00:05:40,639 --> 00:05:42,680
Until the very last moment of the competition,

73
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,360
nothing is certain.

74
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,279
We shall see.

75
00:05:50,079 --> 00:05:53,759
I'm using highly concentrated detoxifying herbs.

76
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:55,439
The effect is stronger,

77
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:56,519
and the detoxification is faster.

78
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,560
What's going on?

79
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:19,879
So much for the Xuanyi Society's prodigy.

80
00:06:19,879 --> 00:06:21,160
Tell me, does this Medicine Holder Li

81
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,439
actually have any real skill?

82
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:24,800
He probably just rode his father's coattails.

83
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:26,560
Impossible. This is absolutely impossible.

84
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:27,920
What's happening here?

85
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:29,959
Flushed complexion.

86
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,759
Abdominal swelling.

87
00:06:31,759 --> 00:06:32,600
The internal toxin can't be identified.

88
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,279
A life is at stake.

89
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:36,279
The competition must be halted immediately.

90
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:39,800
Everyone, rush the patient to the ER now!

91
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,040
Before her condition worsens!

92
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:47,360
Let me try one more time.

93
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,120
My prescription can't be wrong.

94
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:49,639
I'm out of here.

95
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:51,639
The patient isn't your guinea pig.

96
00:06:51,639 --> 00:06:53,720
You'd better look after yourself first.

97
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,519
Move aside.

98
00:06:58,360 --> 00:07:01,959
I've suppressed the Gu worm for you again.

99
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:03,600
This Six Realms Ghost Poison is hard to cure.

100
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,839
When the poison flares up,

101
00:07:06,839 --> 00:07:07,879
you must take this medicine.

102
00:07:07,879 --> 00:07:09,199
The poison will dissipate in three breaths.

103
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:17,199
Move aside!

104
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:20,800
This shouldn't be happening.

105
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:24,040
What's going on?

106
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,120
Quick, film it!

107
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:32,160
Strange.

108
00:07:34,160 --> 00:07:35,560
The poison in her body is gone.

109
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,800
The one I've got my eye on really is intriguing.

110
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,480
Let's go.

111
00:07:41,279 --> 00:07:42,879
It must be my formula that worked.

112
00:07:42,879 --> 00:07:43,759
It has to be.

113
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,680
What on earth happened?

114
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:52,199
I can cure the Gu worm inside you for good.

115
00:07:52,199 --> 00:07:53,439
You don't want to be controlled forever, do you?

116
00:07:53,439 --> 00:07:54,160
Want to sit down and talk?

117
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:57,079
I don't know either.

118
00:08:06,399 --> 00:08:08,000
Miss.

119
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,360
Did you just drink this?

120
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,759
Ten Thousand Poison Gall, Qihuang Grass,

121
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,000
and Spirit Wind Flower.

122
00:08:28,639 --> 00:08:30,079
This is Number 0's prescription.

123
00:08:31,399 --> 00:08:33,159
Number 0 is even more amazing than I thought.

124
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:36,600
Number 0!

125
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,879
Number 0 is even more amazing than I thought.

126
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:38,360
Where's Number 0?

127
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:38,879
What a twist!

128
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:42,879
Did anyone actually see Number 0?

129
00:08:44,279 --> 00:08:45,200
Where did Number 0 go?

130
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:47,000
Looks like the Xuanyi Society has a new rising star.

131
00:08:57,919 --> 00:08:59,159
He sure runs fast.

132
00:09:20,759 --> 00:09:22,200
I'd like to see

133
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:24,639
what else you've got besides medical skills.

134
00:09:27,159 --> 00:09:28,519
The Zhenhai Calming Manual

135
00:09:28,519 --> 00:09:29,480
The Zhenhai Calming Manual is gone!

136
00:09:50,159 --> 00:09:51,559
Miss,

137
00:09:51,559 --> 00:09:53,559
can you tell me what on earth is going on?

138
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:58,720
Alright.

139
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,759
You two, take good care of her.

140
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:03,679
I'll be taking what belongs to me.

141
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:11,320
Who on earth was it?

142
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,919
Who took the Zhenhai Calming Manual?

143
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:16,120
It was that magician contestant!

144
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:25,200
Master Apothecary!

145
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,039
We've found Number 0!

146
00:10:26,919 --> 00:10:28,399
Isn't this Deputy Master Apothecary Cheng?

147
00:10:28,399 --> 00:10:30,720
He looks like he's just recovering from a serious illness.

148
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,039
His pulse is weak.

149
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:41,759
It's definitely not him.

150
00:10:42,559 --> 00:10:44,159
Who's been impersonating Number 0?

151
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:47,120
What a sneaky little rat, pulling a bait-and-switch!

152
00:10:47,759 --> 00:10:48,600
Xuanshui Hall, hear my orders!

153
00:10:50,159 --> 00:10:52,240
Turn this place upside down and find that bumpkin!

154
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:52,919
Yes, sir!

155
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:08,840
Seal off every exit immediately!

156
00:11:09,399 --> 00:11:12,480
Find the thief who stole the Zhenhai Calming Manual!

157
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,879
What a lousy contest.

158
00:11:18,879 --> 00:11:20,080
Why make the venue so huge?

159
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:21,639
I'm exhausted.

160
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,759
I won it fair and square.

161
00:11:28,759 --> 00:11:29,759
That doesn't count as stealing, right?

162
00:11:37,679 --> 00:11:39,480
Why isn't there even an author listed?

163
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:44,559
The Yang family's secret art, the Zhenhai Calming Manual.

164
00:11:46,039 --> 00:11:48,200
This Zhenhai Calming Manual...

165
00:11:48,200 --> 00:11:51,159
It's a thousand-year treasure of the Xuanyi Society!

166
00:11:51,159 --> 00:11:52,080
It seems

167
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,840
to uncover my origins,

168
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,360
I still need to enter the Xuanyi Society.

169
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:58,720
Xiangyang, I'm really not hungry.

170
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:00,159
Can we eat another day?

171
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:01,600
Come on!

172
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,360
Xiangyang!

173
00:12:04,399 --> 00:12:04,720
Hurry up!

174
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:05,720
I'm really not hungry!

175
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:07,480
Can we do it another day?

176
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:09,200
These herbs are important.

177
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,399
The patients are still waiting!

178
00:12:10,399 --> 00:12:11,559
I have to get back to the clinic.

179
00:12:11,559 --> 00:12:12,720
Patients?

180
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,879
So patients matter more than me?

181
00:12:16,799 --> 00:12:18,000
After the contest is over,

182
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,559
all your time belongs to me!

183
00:12:20,879 --> 00:12:21,519
That's going way too far.

184
00:12:21,519 --> 00:12:22,960
Xiangyang,

185
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:23,799
let me deliver these.

186
00:12:23,799 --> 00:12:25,240
I'll come find you right after, okay?

187
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:27,440
Let's go. You're coming with me right now!

188
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,960
Xiangyang, let go!

189
00:12:29,919 --> 00:12:31,039
Come with me!

190
00:12:32,759 --> 00:12:34,440
Hurry up and come with me!

191
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:35,480
Xiangyang!

192
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:41,039
How are you doing your job?

193
00:12:41,039 --> 00:12:42,360
Don't you have eyes?

194
00:12:59,679 --> 00:13:00,720
Young man,

195
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,440
did I get your face dirty?

196
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,399
Here, let me wipe it off for you.

197
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:05,879
Get lost!

198
00:13:09,799 --> 00:13:10,639
Go away!

199
00:13:10,639 --> 00:13:11,360
Scram!

200
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,960
Hey, kid,

201
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:24,519
your little smartwatch is ringing.

202
00:13:24,519 --> 00:13:25,679
Hurry home for dinner,

203
00:13:25,679 --> 00:13:28,240
or your mom will start worrying.

204
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,000
You...

205
00:13:37,759 --> 00:13:39,120
Still not leaving?

206
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:40,200
Do you really wanna go eat with him?

207
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:53,960
This Number 0 is no ordinary guy.

208
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:55,639
He could be useful to me.

209
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,440
Double it.

210
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,279
I'm starting with four Kings.

211
00:14:00,840 --> 00:14:03,000
Pair of Kings and an 8.

212
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:07,039
Who is it?

213
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:08,480
Brother-in-law.

214
00:14:14,799 --> 00:14:15,360
Come here.

215
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:16,200
Brother-in-law.

216
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:16,879
Wipe yourself off.

217
00:14:20,279 --> 00:14:21,159
Hurry up.

218
00:14:21,159 --> 00:14:22,039
Brother-in-law.

219
00:14:22,039 --> 00:14:22,720
Drink your medicine.

220
00:14:39,519 --> 00:14:41,720
Within three days,

221
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:43,600
bring back the Zhenhai Calming Manual.

222
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:46,200
Otherwise,

223
00:14:46,200 --> 00:14:47,799
you'll all die with me!

224
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:49,039
Yes.

225
00:14:49,039 --> 00:14:49,879
Yes, brother-in-law.

226
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,320
Today at the Xuanyi Society's gate,

227
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:05,360
a mysterious, highly skilled Medicine Apprentice

228
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:07,159
saved Miss Lu from danger.

229
00:15:07,159 --> 00:15:09,559
Genius Medicine Holder Li Xiangyang was publicly humiliated.

230
00:15:12,399 --> 00:15:14,480
You're really impressive.

231
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:16,320
How'd you come up with so many tricks?

232
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,600
If that brat hadn't run off so fast,

233
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:20,360
he would've gotten what he deserved.

234
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:33,919
You're quite an interesting person.

235
00:15:38,279 --> 00:15:39,480
Thank you for earlier.

236
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,840
I don't even know your name yet.

237
00:15:48,159 --> 00:15:49,320
Nameless.

238
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:50,639
Nameless?

239
00:15:50,639 --> 00:15:53,600
A name's just a label, it's not important.

240
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:55,480
What matters is what you do.

241
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:04,240
My mistake then.

242
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:06,279
Let me treat my savior to a meal.

243
00:16:06,279 --> 00:16:08,679
And if I could also help my savior

244
00:16:08,679 --> 00:16:10,159
arrange a job, even better.

245
00:16:12,759 --> 00:16:13,480
I...

246
00:16:13,480 --> 00:16:14,639
Just kidding.

247
00:16:14,639 --> 00:16:15,679
If it's inconvenient, forget it.

248
00:16:15,679 --> 00:16:16,879
No,

249
00:16:16,879 --> 00:16:18,080
no problem.

250
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,720
If you don't mind,

251
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:21,200
you can join our Tianzi No. 1 clinic.

252
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:24,000
As a Lu, I can put in a recommendation.

253
00:16:26,559 --> 00:16:28,240
Tianzi No. 1?

254
00:16:29,399 --> 00:16:30,639
Sounds pretty impressive.

255
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:33,639
Tianzi No. 1 is the first clinic opened

256
00:16:33,639 --> 00:16:35,200
after the Xuanyi Society entered the secular world.

257
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:36,840
It's the cradle for nurturing Medicine Masters.

258
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:38,600
With your skills, you'd fit right in.

259
00:16:44,919 --> 00:16:48,519
Looks like I should fill my stomach first.

260
00:16:48,519 --> 00:16:51,639
But could you come deliver some medicine with me first?

261
00:16:51,639 --> 00:16:52,759
Sure, let's go.

262
00:16:52,759 --> 00:16:53,600
Let's go.
